00:29:30,890 --> 00:29:33,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">Only while the blood of my blood lives.</font>

390
00:29:37,599 --> 00:29:41,609
<font color="#FFFFFF">When he dies, she is nothing.</font>

391
00:29:46,650 --> 00:29:52,740
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have never been nothing.
I am the blood of the dragon.</font>

392
00:29:54,410 --> 00:30:00,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">The dragons are all dead, Khaleesi.</font>

393
00:30:07,799 --> 00:30:10,299
<font color="#FFFFFF">I think you should wear your armor tonight, ser.</font>

394
00:30:11,349 --> 00:30:13,099
<font color="#FFFFFF">I think you're right.</font>

395
00:30:18,390 --> 00:30:22,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You've saved me once more.
- And now you must save him.</font>

396
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:24,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's beyond the healer's skills.</font>

397
00:30:24,779 --> 00:30:27,150
<font color="#FFFFFF">All I can do is ease his path.</font>

398
00:30:27,279 --> 00:30:29,450
<font color="#FFFFFF">Save him and I will free you. I swear it.</font>

399
00:30:30,779 --> 00:30:32,660
<font color="#FFFFFF">You must know a way.</font>

400
00:30:33,279 --> 00:30:34,490
<font color="#FFFFFF">Some...</font>

401
00:30:35,869 --> 00:30:37,200
<font color="#FFFFFF">Some magic.</font>

402
00:30:39,329 --> 00:30:41,000
<font color="#FFFFFF">There is a spell.</font>

403
00:30:42,039 --> 00:30:44,380
<font color="#FFFFFF">Some would say death is cleaner.</font>

404
00:30:54,309 --> 00:30:55,970
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do it.</font>

405
00:30:56,849 --> 00:30:58,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">Save him.</font>

406
00:30:58,690 --> 00:31:01,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">- There is a price.
- You'll have gold, whatever you want.</font>

407
00:31:01,599 --> 00:31:03,859
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not a matter of gold.
This is bloodmagic.</font>

408
00:31:03,980 --> 00:31:05,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">Only death pays for life.</font>

409
00:31:09,490 --> 00:31:11,029
<font color="#FFFFFF">My death?</font>

410
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:13,910
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, not your death, Khaleesi.</font>

411
00:31:15,619 --> 00:31:17,289
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bring me his horse.</font>

412
00:31:40,849 --> 00:31:42,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">Khaleesi, do not do this thing.</font>

413
00:31:42,690 --> 00:31:45,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Let me kill this witch.
- Kill her and you kill your khal.</font>

414
00:31:46,109 --> 00:31:49,029
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is bloodmagic.
It is forbidden.</font>

415
00:31:49,150 --> 00:31:52,740
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am your khaleesi.
I tell you what is forbidden.</font>

416
00:32:03,289 --> 00:32:04,460
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go. Now.</font>

417
00:32:04,579 --> 00:32:06,460
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Take her and leave.
- Uh-uh.</font>

418
00:32:06,589 --> 00:32:07,750
<font color="#FFFFFF">Take her!</font>

419
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:17,549
<font color="#FFFFFF">You must go also, lady. Once I begin to sing,
no one must enter the tent.</font>

420
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:20,220
<font color="#FFFFFF">The dead will dance here tonight.</font>

421
00:32:33,609 --> 00:32:35,319
<font color="#FFFFFF">No one will enter.</font>

422
00:32:43,579 --> 00:32:45,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bring him back to me.</font>

423
00:33:02,430 --> 00:33:04,099
<font color="#FFFFFF">What have you done?</font>

424
00:33:04,230 --> 00:33:06,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have to save him.</font>

425
00:33:06,599 --> 00:33:09,859
<font color="#FFFFFF">We could have been 10 miles
away from here by now, on the way to Asshai.</font>

426
00:33:09,980 --> 00:33:11,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">You would have been safe.</font>

427
00:33:20,450 --> 00:33:21,700
<font color="#FFFFFF">This must not be.</font>

428
00:33:21,829 --> 00:33:23,329
<font color="#FFFFFF">This must be.</font>

429
00:33:23,450 --> 00:33:24,660
<font color="#FFFFFF">Witch.</font>

430
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, you can't.</font>

431
00:33:28,750 --> 00:33:30,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">Khaleesi!</font>

432
00:33:32,130 --> 00:33:34,460
<font color="#FFFFFF">No further, horselord.</font>

433
00:34:15,340 --> 00:34:16,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you hurt?</font>

434
00:34:16,590 --> 00:34:17,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">- The baby...
- Hmm?</font>

435
00:34:17,679 --> 00:34:19,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">.. is coming.</font>

436
00:34:19,429 --> 00:34:23,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Fetch the midwives.
- They will not come. They say she is cursed.</font>

437
00:34:24,679 --> 00:34:26,809
<font color="#FFFFFF">They'll come or I'll have their heads.</font>

438
00:34:28,139 --> 00:34:31,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">The witch - she can bring baby.
I hear her say so.</font>

439
00:34:55,170 --> 00:34:56,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you in agony, my lion?</font>

440
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:59,380
<font color="#FFFFFF">- No.
- You look like you're in agony.</font>

441
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:02,889
<font color="#FFFFFF">The fire is burning your pretty soft skin.</font>

442
00:35:06,559 --> 00:35:08,139
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ah!</font>

443
00:35:09,889 --> 00:35:12,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">Damn you, woman.
Are you immune to pain?</font>

444
00:35:12,559 --> 00:35:14,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Just used to it.
- Drink.</font>

445
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:18,739
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's play a new game.</font>

446
00:35:20,239 --> 00:35:22,820
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's a Braavosi knife game
I could teach you.</font>

447
00:35:22,949 --> 00:35:26,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">Does it involve the potential
for losing fingers?</font>

448
00:35:26,159 --> 00:35:28,659
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Not if you win.
- No!</font>

449
00:35:28,789 --> 00:35:31,329
<font color="#FFFFFF">No fire games, no knife games.</font>

450
00:35:32,250 --> 00:35:36,289
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Let's do something I'm good at.
- What are you good at?</font>

451
00:35:36,420 --> 00:35:38,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">I happen to be a great judge of character.</font>

452
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:40,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">- This sounds like a boring game.
- It's not.</font>

453
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:44,849
<font color="#FFFFFF">Here's how it works -
I make a statement about your past.</font>

454
00:35:44,969 --> 00:35:48,099
<font color="#FFFFFF">if I'm right, you drink.
if I'm wrong, I drink.</font>

455
00:35:48,219 --> 00:35:51,099
<font color="#FFFFFF">And no lying.
I'll know if you're lying.</font>

456
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:53,059
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't want to play this game.</font>

457
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:55,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fine. Bronn first.</font>

458
00:35:59,780 --> 00:36:01,570
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your father beat you.</font>

459
00:36:07,199 --> 00:36:09,239
<font color="#FFFFFF">But my mother hit harder.</font>

460
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:15,170
<font color="#FFFFFF">You killed your first man
before you were 12.</font>

461
00:36:15,289 --> 00:36:17,090
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was a woman.</font>

462
00:36:20,380 --> 00:36:21,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">She swung an axe at me.</font>

463
00:36:23,469 --> 00:36:25,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">You've been north of the Wall.</font>

464
00:36:28,469 --> 00:36:30,139
<font color="#FFFFFF">What brought you up there?</font>

465
00:36:31,769 --> 00:36:33,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Work.
- And...</font>

466
00:36:34,690 --> 00:36:38,019
<font color="#FFFFFF">you once loved a woman many years ago,
but it turned out badly</font>

467
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:39,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">so you've never let yourself love again.</font>

468
00:36:41,820 --> 00:36:44,150
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, wait, that's me.</font>

469
00:36:47,409 --> 00:36:50,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your turn, my mysterious foreign beauty.</font>

470
00:36:50,289 --> 00:36:51,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't want to play.</font>

471
00:36:51,949 --> 00:36:55,710
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's fun! Look at the fun we're having.</font>

472
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:01,340
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your mother was a whore.</font>

473
00:37:02,340 --> 00:37:03,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">Drink.</font>

474
00:37:10,099 --> 00:37:12,179
<font color="#FFFFFF">All right.</font>

475
00:37:12,309 --> 00:37:15,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your father left the family when
you were very young, never to return.</font>

476
00:37:15,849 --> 00:37:16,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">Drink.</font>

477
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:21,019
<font color="#FFFFFF">- And we've established the rules about lying?
- Drink!</font>

478
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:25,949
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mm.</font>

479
00:37:28,489 --> 00:37:29,989
<font color="#FFFFFF">You wanted a different life.</font>

480
00:37:30,119 --> 00:37:32,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">You came from somewhere
and you wanted to be elsewhere.</font>

481
00:37:32,949 --> 00:37:35,619
<font color="#FFFFFF">The whole shit-stained world
could drink off that one.</font>

482
00:37:35,750 --> 00:37:37,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">So, specifics...</font>

483
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:41,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">You wanted to be elsewhere,
but how would you get there?</font>

484
00:37:41,550 --> 00:37:45,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't believe the life
of the Silent Sisters is for you.</font>

485
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:49,090
<font color="#FFFFFF">So... what's a lowborn girl to do?</font>

486
00:37:52,769 --> 00:37:54,019
<font color="#FFFFFF">Drink.</font>

487
00:37:56,849 --> 00:37:58,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Are you sure...
- Drink!</font>

488
00:38:04,150 --> 00:38:07,949
<font color="#FFFFFF">And don't talk about
my mother and father ever,</font>

489
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:10,570
<font color="#FFFFFF">or I will carve your eyes from your head.</font>

490
00:38:15,079 --> 00:38:18,000
<font color="#FFFFFF">My dear lady,
if I have offended you, I apologize.</font>

491
00:38:19,170 --> 00:38:20,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">My turn.</font>

492
00:38:20,250 --> 00:38:22,289
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fine, fine.</font>

493
00:38:22,420 --> 00:38:23,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ask away.</font>

494
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:27,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">Try to penetrate the enigma that is me.</font>

495
00:38:27,800 --> 00:38:30,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Who were you in love with?
- That's not how the game works.</font>

496
00:38:30,849 --> 00:38:33,179
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't care the way the game works.</font>

497
00:38:33,309 --> 00:38:35,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">Our lord here used to be married.</font>

498
00:38:36,269 --> 00:38:38,349
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Married?
- How did you hear that?</font>

499
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:41,769
<font color="#FFFFFF">You hear lots of things
playing dice with Lannister soldiers.</font>

500
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">Another night, perhaps.</font>

501
00:38:47,110 --> 00:38:49,070
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not another night. This night.</font>

502
00:38:50,610 --> 00:38:52,239
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not a pleasant story.</font>

503
00:38:54,239 --> 00:38:55,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, maybe I will cry.</font>

504
00:38:55,949 --> 00:39:00,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm guessing the lady and I can tell more
unpleasant stories than your lordship.</font>

505
00:39:02,590 --> 00:39:04,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">So...</font>

506
00:39:08,050 --> 00:39:13,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was 16. My brother Jaime and I were riding,
when we heard a scream.</font>

507
00:39:13,889 --> 00:39:18,349
<font color="#FFFFFF">She ran out onto the road,
clothes half torn off, with two men on her heels.</font>

508
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:22,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">Jaime scared away the men easily enough,
while I wrapped her in my cloak.</font>

509
00:39:23,110 --> 00:39:24,900
<font color="#FFFFFF">She was too scared to send off on her own,</font>

510
00:39:25,019 --> 00:39:30,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">so while Jaime hunted down the rapers
I took her to the nearest inn and fed her.</font>

511
00:39:30,150 --> 00:39:32,530
<font color="#FFFFFF">Her name was Tysha.</font>

512
00:39:32,659 --> 00:39:34,820
<font color="#FFFFFF">She was a wheelwright's orphan.</font>

513
00:39:34,949 --> 00:39:37,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">And she was hungry.</font>

514
00:39:37,239 --> 00:39:40,500
<font color="#FFFFFF">Together we finished off three chickens
and a flagon of wine.</font>

515
00:39:40,619 --> 00:39:44,789
<font color="#FFFFFF">lmpossible as it seems, there was a time
when I was unaccustomed to wine.</font>

516
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:48,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">I forgot how afraid I was around girls...</font>

517
00:39:48,170 --> 00:39:51,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">how I was always waiting
for them to laugh at me or...</font>

518
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:52,929
<font color="#FFFFFF">look away embarrassed,</font>

519
00:39:53,050 --> 00:39:55,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">or ask me about my tall, handsome brother.</font>

520
00:39:55,849 --> 00:39:58,179
<font color="#FFFFFF">I forgot about everything but Tysha.</font>

521
00:39:59,429 --> 00:40:02,230
<font color="#FFFFFF">And somehow I found myself in her bed.</font>

522
00:40:02,349 --> 00:40:05,230
<font color="#FFFFFF">For three chickens, I should hope so.</font>

523
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:08,400
<font color="#FFFFFF">It didn't last long.
I didn't know what the hell I was doing.</font>

524
00:40:08,530 --> 00:40:10,860
<font color="#FFFFFF">But she was good to me.</font>

525
00:40:10,989 --> 00:40:12,949
<font color="#FFFFFF">She kissed me afterwards and...</font>

526
00:40:13,989 --> 00:40:15,449
<font color="#FFFFFF">sang me a song.</font>

527
00:40:17,079 --> 00:40:20,579
<font color="#FFFFFF">And by morning
I was deep enough in love to ask for her hand.</font>

528
00:40:21,579 --> 00:40:23,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">A few lies, a few gold coins,
one drunken septon</font>

529
00:40:24,079 --> 00:40:26,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">and there you have it - man and wife.</font>

530
00:40:27,550 --> 00:40:32,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">For a fortnight anyway,
until the septon sobered up and told my father.</font>

531
00:40:32,380 --> 00:40:34,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, I imagine that was the end of all that.</font>

532
00:40:35,010 --> 00:40:36,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not quite.</font>

533
00:40:37,889 --> 00:40:40,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">First, my father had Jaime tell me the truth.</font>

534
00:40:42,730 --> 00:40:44,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">The girl was a whore, you see.</font>

535
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:51,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">Jaime had arranged the whole thing -
the road, the rapers... all of it.</font>

536
00:40:51,570 --> 00:40:54,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">He thought it was time I had a woman.</font>

537
00:40:56,159 --> 00:40:58,239
<font color="#FFFFFF">After my brother confessed...</font>

538
00:40:59,539 --> 00:41:01,369
<font color="#FFFFFF">my father brought in my wife</font>

539
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:03,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">and gave her to his guards.</font>

540
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:07,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">He paid her well -
a silver for each man.</font>

541
00:41:07,789 --> 00:41:10,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">How many whores command
that kind of price?</font>

542
00:41:12,590 --> 00:41:15,969
<font color="#FFFFFF">He brought me into the barracks
and made me watch.</font>

543
00:41:16,090 --> 00:41:19,429
<font color="#FFFFFF">By the end, she had so much silver</font>

544
00:41:19,559 --> 00:41:24,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">that the coins were slipping through her fingers
and rolling on to the floor.</font>

545
00:41:28,230 --> 00:41:31,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">I would have killed the man
who did that to me.</font>

546
00:41:32,070 --> 00:41:34,239
<font color="#FFFFFF">You should have known she was a whore.</font>

547
00:41:35,110 --> 00:41:36,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">Really?</font>

548
00:41:37,030 --> 00:41:39,489
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was 16, drunk and in love.</font>

549
00:41:39,619 --> 00:41:44,949
<font color="#FFFFFF">A girl who was almost raped doesn't invite
another man into her bed two hours later.</font>

550
00:41:46,039 --> 00:41:49,579
<font color="#FFFFFF">As I said, I was young and stupid.</font>

551
00:41:52,300 --> 00:41:54,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">You are still young and stupid.</font>

552
00:42:18,360 --> 00:42:20,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hyah!</font>

553
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:40,219
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What is it? What do you want?
- You're sleeping through the war.</font>

554
00:42:40,340 --> 00:42:43,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What?
- They stole a night's march on us.</font>

555
00:42:43,179 --> 00:42:44,679
<font color="#FFFFFF">They're a mile north.</font>

556
00:42:45,519 --> 00:42:47,889
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Get my squire!
- You don't have a squire.</font>

557
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:52,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">if I die, weep for me.</font>

558
00:42:53,690 --> 00:42:56,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">You'll be dead.
How will you know?</font>

559
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:04,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll know.</font>

560
00:43:07,079 --> 00:43:08,619
<font color="#FFFFFF">Watch out! Move!</font>

561
00:43:09,750 --> 00:43:11,369
<font color="#FFFFFF">Out of the way!</font>

562
00:43:11,500 --> 00:43:13,380
<font color="#FFFFFF">Move aside!</font>

563
00:43:19,800 --> 00:43:21,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stay low.</font>

564
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:23,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stay low?</font>

565
00:43:23,929 --> 00:43:26,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">if you're lucky, no one will notice you.</font>

566
00:43:26,389 --> 00:43:28,219
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was born lucky.</font>

567
00:43:31,440 --> 00:43:33,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tribesmen of the Vale,</font>

568
00:43:33,860 --> 00:43:35,150
<font color="#FFFFFF">gather round!</font>

569
00:43:36,900 --> 00:43:39,280
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stone Crows!</font>

570
00:43:39,400 --> 00:43:41,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">Black Ears!
Burned Men!</font>

571
00:43:41,739 --> 00:43:44,320
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Moon Brothers!
- And Painted Dogs!</font>

572
00:43:44,449 --> 00:43:47,239
<font color="#FFFFFF">- And Painted Dogs!
- Painted Dogs!</font>

573
00:43:47,369 --> 00:43:50,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your dominion over the Vale begins now!</font>

574
00:43:50,369 --> 00:43:53,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">Onward, to claim what is yours!</font>

575
00:43:53,329 --> 00:43:55,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">Half man! Half man!</font>

576
00:43:55,539 --> 00:43:58,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">Half man! Half man!</font>

577
00:43:58,960 --> 00:44:01,590
<font color="#FFFFFF">Half man! Half man!</font>

578
00:44:01,719 --> 00:44:03,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">To battle!</font>

579
00:44:46,099 --> 00:44:47,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're a shit warrior.</font>

580
00:44:51,099 --> 00:44:52,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm alive?</font>

581
00:44:53,440 --> 00:44:54,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're alive.</font>

582
00:45:00,440 --> 00:45:02,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did we win?</font>

583
00:45:02,150 --> 00:45:04,820
<font color="#FFFFFF">We wouldn't be having
this conversation if we didn't.</font>

584
00:45:17,880 --> 00:45:20,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">How did our tribesmen do?</font>

585
00:45:21,670 --> 00:45:23,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah, good.</font>

586
00:45:24,929 --> 00:45:29,179
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's nice to see them getting along.
You're wounded.</font>

587
00:45:30,349 --> 00:45:32,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good of you to notice.</font>

588
00:45:33,179 --> 00:45:34,429
<font color="#FFFFFF">I hear we won.</font>

589
00:45:34,559 --> 00:45:37,099
<font color="#FFFFFF">Huh! The scouts were wrong.</font>

590
00:45:38,019 --> 00:45:40,900
<font color="#FFFFFF">There were 2,000 Stark bannermen, not 20.</font>

591
00:45:41,940 --> 00:45:44,070
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did we get the Stark boy, at least?</font>

592
00:45:44,190 --> 00:45:45,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">He wasn't here.</font>

593
00:45:46,489 --> 00:45:48,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where was he?</font>

594
00:45:48,320 --> 00:45:50,699
<font color="#FFFFFF">With his other 18,000 men.</font>

595
00:45:54,369 --> 00:45:56,500
<font color="#FFFFFF">And where are they?</font>

596
00:46:06,630 --> 00:46:08,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">- We should go, my lady.
- No!</font>

597
00:46:13,969 --> 00:46:15,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">My lady!</font>

598
00:46:17,559 --> 00:46:19,769
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hyah! Hyah!</font>

599
00:46:50,929 --> 00:46:55,059
<font color="#FFFFFF">By the time they knew what was happening,
it had already happened.</font>

600
00:46:58,440 --> 00:47:02,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lady Stark. I'd offer you my sword,
but I seem to have lost it.</font>

601
00:47:02,610 --> 00:47:04,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">It is not your sword I want.</font>

602
00:47:06,070 --> 00:47:07,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">Give me my daughters back.</font>

603
00:47:07,780 --> 00:47:09,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">Give me my husband.</font>

604
00:47:10,449 --> 00:47:12,239
<font color="#FFFFFF">I've lost them too, I'm afraid.</font>

605
00:47:12,369 --> 00:47:14,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">Kill him, Robb.
Send his head to his father.</font>

606
00:47:14,949 --> 00:47:19,710
<font color="#FFFFFF">- He cut down ten of our men. You saw him.
- He's more use to us alive than dead.</font>

607
00:47:19,829 --> 00:47:22,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">Take him away and put him in irons.</font>

608
00:47:23,039 --> 00:47:25,500
<font color="#FFFFFF">We could end this war right now, boy,</font>

609
00:47:25,630 --> 00:47:27,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">save thousands of lives.</font>

610
00:47:27,760 --> 00:47:30,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">You fight for the Starks,
I fight for the Lannisters.</font>

611
00:47:30,760 --> 00:47:32,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">Swords or lances, teeth, nails -</font>

612
00:47:32,849 --> 00:47:36,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">choose your weapons
and let's end this here and now.</font>

613
00:47:39,099 --> 00:47:41,230
<font color="#FFFFFF">if we do it your way, Kingslayer...</font>

614
00:47:42,309 --> 00:47:44,019
<font color="#FFFFFF">you'd win.</font>

615
00:47:47,150 --> 00:47:48,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're not doing it your way.</font>

616
00:47:50,530 --> 00:47:52,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, pretty man.</font>

617
00:48:01,420 --> 00:48:06,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I sent 2,000 men to their graves today.
- The bards will sing songs of their sacrifice.</font>

618
00:48:06,340 --> 00:48:09,340
<font color="#FFFFFF">Aye. But the dead won't hear them.</font>

619
00:48:16,349 --> 00:48:19,059
<font color="#FFFFFF">One victory does not make us conquerors.</font>

620
00:48:20,849 --> 00:48:22,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did we free my father?</font>

621
00:48:23,980 --> 00:48:26,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did we rescue my sisters from the queen?</font>

622
00:48:27,980 --> 00:48:31,530
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did we free the North from those
who want us on our knees?</font>

623
00:48:37,030 --> 00:48:39,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">This war is far from over.</font>

624
00:49:10,530 --> 00:49:12,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">Could I have one?</font>

625
00:49:12,239 --> 00:49:13,989
<font color="#FFFFFF">A lemon one... or any of them.</font>

626
00:49:14,110 --> 00:49:15,739
<font color="#FFFFFF">Three coppers.</font>

627
00:49:16,570 --> 00:49:20,239
<font color="#FFFFFF">- How about a nice fat pigeon?
- Oh, piss off now. Go on.</font>

628
00:49:21,329 --> 00:49:24,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you have any stale ones from yesterday?
Or any burnt ones?</font>

629
00:49:24,289 --> 00:49:25,750
<font color="#FFFFFF">Piss off!</font>

630
00:49:33,130 --> 00:49:35,170
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, where's everyone going?
What's happening?</font>

631
00:49:35,300 --> 00:49:37,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">- They're taking him to the Sept of Baelor.
- Who?</font>

632
00:49:37,590 --> 00:49:39,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">The Hand of the King.</font>

633
00:50:46,960 --> 00:50:49,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Traitor!
- Coward!</font>

634
00:50:49,250 --> 00:50:51,289
<font color="#FFFFFF">Baelor.</font>

635
00:50:51,420 --> 00:50:52,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">Baelor!</font>

636
00:50:58,380 --> 00:51:01,010
<font color="#FFFFFF">Traitor! Traitor!</font>

637
00:51:21,159 --> 00:51:23,369
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am Eddard Stark...</font>

638
00:51:23,489 --> 00:51:25,489
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lord of Winterfell...</font>

639
00:51:25,619 --> 00:51:27,949
<font color="#FFFFFF">and Hand of the King.</font>

640
00:51:37,170 --> 00:51:39,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">I come before you to confess my treason...</font>

641
00:51:40,840 --> 00:51:42,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">in the sight of gods and men.</font>

642
00:51:44,719 --> 00:51:46,389
<font color="#FFFFFF">I betrayed the faith of my king...</font>

643
00:51:47,519 --> 00:51:49,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">and the trust of my friend Robert.</font>

644
00:51:50,940 --> 00:51:53,400
<font color="#FFFFFF">I swore to protect and defend his children.</font>

645
00:51:54,360 --> 00:51:56,400
<font color="#FFFFFF">But before his blood was cold...</font>

646
00:51:57,400 --> 00:52:00,150
<font color="#FFFFFF">I plotted to murder his son...</font>

647
00:52:00,280 --> 00:52:02,780
<font color="#FFFFFF">and seize the throne for myself.</font>

648
00:52:13,250 --> 00:52:19,090
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let the High Septon and Baelor the Blessed
bear witness to what I say...</font>

649
00:52:22,219 --> 00:52:24,179
<font color="#FFFFFF">Joffrey Baratheon...</font>

650
00:52:25,260 --> 00:52:27,429
<font color="#FFFFFF">is the one true heir to the Iron Throne...</font>

651
00:52:28,559 --> 00:52:30,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">by the grace of all the gods,</font>

652
00:52:31,099 --> 00:52:33,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lord of the Seven Kingdoms...</font>

653
00:52:33,440 --> 00:52:35,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">and Protector of the Realm.</font>

654
00:52:43,070 --> 00:52:44,989
<font color="#FFFFFF">As... As we sin...</font>

655
00:52:45,820 --> 00:52:47,489
<font color="#FFFFFF">so do we suffer.</font>

656
00:52:47,619 --> 00:52:50,659
<font color="#FFFFFF">This man has confessed his crimes...</font>

657
00:52:50,789 --> 00:52:53,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">in sight of gods and men.</font>

658
00:52:53,920 --> 00:52:56,500
<font color="#FFFFFF">The gods are just...</font>

659
00:52:56,630 --> 00:53:00,090
<font color="#FFFFFF">but beloved Baelor taught us...</font>

660
00:53:00,210 --> 00:53:02,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">they can also be merciful.</font>

661
00:53:06,139 --> 00:53:10,219
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is to be done
with this traitor, Your Grace?</font>

662
00:53:15,150 --> 00:53:18,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">My mother wishes me
to let Lord Eddard join the Night's Watch.</font>

663
00:53:18,320 --> 00:53:23,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stripped of all titles and powers,
he would serve the realm in permanent exile.</font>

664
00:53:23,780 --> 00:53:27,820
<font color="#FFFFFF">And my Lady Sansa...
has begged mercy for her father.</font>

665
00:53:32,539 --> 00:53:34,909
<font color="#FFFFFF">But they have the soft hearts of women.</font>

666
00:53:36,250 --> 00:53:38,170
<font color="#FFFFFF">So long as I am your king...</font>

667
00:53:38,289 --> 00:53:41,090
<font color="#FFFFFF">treason shall never go unpunished.</font>

668
00:53:42,170 --> 00:53:43,340
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ser llyn...</font>

669
00:53:44,670 --> 00:53:45,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">bring me his head!</font>

670
00:53:45,969 --> 00:53:48,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

671
00:53:48,179 --> 00:53:50,010
<font color="#FFFFFF">Someone stop him!</font>

672
00:54:01,320 --> 00:54:03,280
<font color="#FFFFFF">My son, this is madness.</font>

673
00:54:04,239 --> 00:54:05,489
<font color="#FFFFFF">Put him down!</font>

674
00:54:12,869 --> 00:54:15,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Don't look!
- Let me go! Let me go!</font>

675
00:54:15,329 --> 00:54:17,869
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shut your mouth!
Look at me! Look at me!</font>

676
00:54:18,000 --> 00:54:20,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop! Daddy! Stop!</font>

677
00:54:20,539 --> 00:54:22,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">- No! No!
- Traitor!</font>

678
00:54:22,550 --> 00:54:23,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop!</font>

679
00:54:27,469 --> 00:54:29,090
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop him! Stop!</font>

